The paper deals with video moment retrieval, which involves natural language processing and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a semantic completion module, which involves natural language processing and could potentially fall under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves information retrieval, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves algorithm design and optimization, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
